body.raw:
Brutalist London is an index of significant Brutalist buildings and landscapes across London.

We prioritise:

- Civic and cultural importance
- Architectural quality and integrity
- Public access and documentary photography

Photo credits: We aim to use our own or freely-licensed monochrome photography. For any corrections, please reach out via Submit.
